#. <section class="sutta" id="sn36.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn36.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 36"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 36"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Sagāthāvagga"
msgstr "1. With Verses"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn36.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Pahānasutta"
msgstr "3. Giving Up"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.3:1.1"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, vedanā."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three feelings."

msgctxt "sn36.3:1.2"
msgid "Katamā tisso?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "sn36.3:1.3"
msgid "Sukhā vedanā, dukkhā vedanā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā."
msgstr "Pleasant, painful, and neutral feeling."

msgctxt "sn36.3:1.4"
msgid ""
"Sukhāya, bhikkhave, vedanāya rāgānusayo pahātabbo, dukkhāya vedanāya "
"paṭighānusayo pahātabbo, adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya avijjānusayo pahātabbo."
msgstr ""
"The underlying tendency to greed should be given up when it comes to "
"pleasant feeling. The underlying tendency to repulsion should be given up "
"when it comes to painful feeling. The underlying tendency to ignorance "
"should be given up when it comes to neutral feeling."

#. VAR: acchecchi → acchejji (s1-3, pts1)
#. VAR: vivattayi → vāvattayi (bj)
msgctxt "sn36.3:1.5"
msgid ""
"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno sukhāya vedanāya rāgānusayo pahīno hoti, "
"dukkhāya vedanāya paṭighānusayo pahīno hoti, adukkhamasukhāya vedanāya "
"avijjānusayo pahīno hoti, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, ‘bhikkhu niranusayo "
"sammaddaso acchecchi taṇhaṃ, vivattayi saṃyojanaṃ, sammā mānābhisamayā "
"antamakāsi dukkhassā’ti."
msgstr ""
"When a mendicant has given up these underlying tendencies, they’re called a "
"mendicant without underlying tendencies, who sees rightly, has cut off "
"craving, untied the fetters, and by rightly comprehending conceit has made "
"an end of suffering.”"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: vedayamānassa → vediyamānassa (bj, pts1)
msgctxt "sn36.3:2.1"
msgid "Sukhaṃ vedayamānassa,"
msgstr "“When you feel pleasure"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:2.2"
msgid "vedanaṃ appajānato;"
msgstr "without understanding feeling,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:2.3"
msgid "So rāgānusayo hoti,"
msgstr "the underlying tendency to greed is there,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:2.4"
msgid "anissaraṇadassino."
msgstr "if you don’t see the escape."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.3:3.1"
msgid "Dukkhaṃ vedayamānassa,"
msgstr "When you feel pain"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:3.2"
msgid "vedanaṃ appajānato;"
msgstr "without understanding feeling,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:3.3"
msgid "Paṭighānusayo hoti,"
msgstr "the underlying tendency to repulsion is there,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:3.4"
msgid "anissaraṇadassino."
msgstr "if you don’t see the escape."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.3:4.1"
msgid "Adukkhamasukhaṃ santaṃ,"
msgstr "As for that peaceful, neutral feeling:"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:4.2"
msgid "bhūripaññena desitaṃ;"
msgstr "he of vast wisdom has taught"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:4.3"
msgid "Tañcāpi abhinandati,"
msgstr "that if you relish it,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:4.4"
msgid "neva dukkhā pamuccati."
msgstr "you’re still not released from suffering."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pli4.206"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.3:5.1"
msgid "Yato ca bhikkhu ātāpī,"
msgstr "But when a mendicant is keen,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:5.2"
msgid "sampajaññaṃ na riñcati;"
msgstr "not neglecting situational awareness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:5.3"
msgid "Tato so vedanā sabbā,"
msgstr "that astute person"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:5.4"
msgid "parijānāti paṇḍito."
msgstr "understands all feelings."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn36.3:6.1"
msgid "So vedanā pariññāya,"
msgstr "Completely understanding feelings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:6.2"
msgid "diṭṭhe dhamme anāsavo;"
msgstr "they’re without defilements in this very life."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:6.3"
msgid "Kāyassa bhedā dhammaṭṭho,"
msgstr "That knowledge-master is grounded in the teaching;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn36.3:6.4"
msgid "saṅkhyaṃ nopeti vedagū”ti."
msgstr "when their body breaks up, they can’t be reckoned.”"

#. </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn36.3:6.5"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
